{
  "stem": "11771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These Jews make it prepare, ready make it a little wider, and a little bigger, in order-- they figure out, they know already.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And man is going to fit him into graves all around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In all the four corners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And when I came in, when we came in at the graves, we saw a mountain of clothes, shoes-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] piled up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They used to take four lines, 20 people, and keep the rest behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They let the 20 people undressed, chase them with the dogs or with the beatings of sticks, close to the graves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And what I saw behind the bundle of the clothes was sitting a German on a bow of kerosene, of gasoline.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A foot, and foot like this one, on the machine gun, on his leg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was sitting like hunting-- hunting dogs, or shooting and hunting birds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He don't care if it's children, or men, or humans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Blah, blah, blah, zoom, zoom, zoom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Killed this 20.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The rest while-- meanwhile-- they are coming to the graves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the second line, undressed and was chased.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] We undressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] On my left side, like I told you, was my rabbi of the Talmud, rabbi [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Somehow he got faster undressed than I am, or my father, who was in the first line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Anyway, he came-- he became to go to the grave in front of me, because I wasn't so fast to be undressed and my father also.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My brother, he [INAUDIBLE], my brother didn't let off my father for a second.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Whatever he did, he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Wanting, grabbed him by the right leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He wouldn't let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he's schlepping him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
